localizedDescription: Gained from achieving Honor Level 5. Craft into Honor-specific rewards. Tokens are earned once per season and do not expire.
localizedRecipeSubtitle: Forge your Honor 5 tokens into the highest tier of Honor rewards. New rewards will be added each season.

localizedDescription: Rare crafting essence. Can be forged into a variety of rare items, which rotate periodically. Click to see the current list of craftable items and when new items will appear.
localizedRecipeSubtitle: Unlock new and classic content exclusively for Mythic Essence. Inventory rotates with new patches.
